Accenture.label: Accenture

České dráhy.label: České dráhy

Barilla Group.label: Barilla Group
Barilla Group.description: Barilla S.p.A. is an Italian and European food company. Wikipedia

Bank of Montreal.label: Bank of Montreal

Bank Leumi.label: Bank Leumi
Bank Leumi.description: Bank Leumi is an Israeli bank. It was founded in London as the Anglo Palestine Company on February 27, 1902, by members of the Zionist movement to promote the industry, construction, agriculture, and ... Wikipedia

Altec Lansing.label: Altec Lansing

American Type Founders.label: American Type Founders

Bank Hapoalim.label: Bank Hapoalim
Bank Hapoalim.description: Bank Hapoalim is Israel’s largest bank. The Bank has a significant presence in global financial markets. Wikipedia

Beechcraft.label: Beechcraft
Beechcraft.description: Beechcraft Corporation is an American manufacturer of general aviation and military aircraft, ranging from light single-engined aircraft to twin-engined turboprop transports, and military trainers. Wikipedia

Ben & Jerry's.label: Ben & Jerry's

Bibby Line.label: Bibby Line
Bibby Line.description:
Bibby Line is a UK company concerned with shipping and marine operations.

Beiersdorf.label: Beiersdorf
Beiersdorf.description: Beiersdorf AG is a German personal care company based in Hamburg, manufacturing personal care products. Its brands include Elastoplast, Eucerin, Labello, La Prairie and Nivea. Wikipedia

Bata Shoes.label: Bata Shoes

Bank of America.label: Bank of America Corporation

Bang & Olufsen.label: Bang & Olufsen
Bang & Olufsen.description: Bang & Olufsen is a Danish company that designs and manufactures audio products, television sets and telephones. Wikipedia

Berlin European UK.label: Berlin European UK

August Storck.label: August Storck

Air Dolomiti.label: Air Dolomiti

Bally Technologies.label: Bally Technologies

Baboo (airline).label: Baboo
Baboo (airline).description: Fly Baboo SA, marketed as Baboo, was a regional airline based on the grounds of Geneva International Airport and in Grand-Saconnex, Switzerland. Wikipedia

BOTAŞ.label: BOTAŞ

Avex Trax.label: Avex Trax
Avex Trax.description: Avex Trax is a record label owned by Japanese entertainment conglomerate Avex Group. The label was launched in September 1990, and was the first label by the Group. Wikipedia

Auto Union.label: Auto Union
Auto Union.description: Auto Union AG, Chemnitz, was an amalgamation of four German automobile manufacturers, founded in 1932 and established in 1936 in Chemnitz, Saxony, during the Great Depression. Wikipedia

Air Cairo.label: Air Cairo

Air Uganda.label: Air Uganda

Atlanta Bread Company.label: Atlanta Bread Company

Australian Securities Exchange.label: ASX

Bharat Earth Movers.label: Bharat Earth Movers

AstroTurf.label: AstroTurf

Atlas Blue.label: Atlas Blue

Bangkok Airways.label: Bangkok Airways

Astra (company).label: Astra International

Behringer.label: Behringer

Air Zimbabwe.label: Air Zimbabwe

Arab Satellite Communications Organizati.label: Arab Satellite Communications Organization

AkzoNobel.label: Akzo Nobel

Air Malawi.label: Air Malawi

Air Koryo.label: Air Koryo

Ariolasoft.label: Ariolasoft

Air Slovakia.label: Air Slovakia

Air Bremen.label: Air Bremen

Alenia Aermacchi.description: Alenia Aermacchi is an Italian aerospace company. A subsidiary of Finmeccanica, the company head office is in Venegono Superiore, Varese. Wikipedia

Astar Air Cargo.label: Astar Air Cargo

AgustaWestland.label: AgustaWestland

Alienware.label: Alienware

Air Arabia.label: Air Arabia

Aero Lloyd Flugreisen GmbH & Co, operated as Aero Lloyd, was a German charter airline based in Oberursel, Germany.

ABB Group.label: ABB Ltd

7th Level.label: 7th Level

Airbus Military.label: Airbus Military

AM General.label: AM General

ARY Group.label: ARY Group

Adnams Brewery.label: Adnams Brewery

A&W Restaurants.label: A&W Restaurants

AVG Technologies.label: AVG
